gmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2871766c64ffd0eaddf662efb394efbb8ea170","tid":299804,"uid":38316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T00:15:22.000Z","msg":"軟件台有一半既post都係John Linux<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b4e255d8e9b038baceafdce20830d7e7bf8941","tid":299804,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T01:16:28.000Z","msg":"保護知識產權有唔同方法，可以用版權，專利話者用商業秘密（trade secret）。如果產品係open source，就唔可以用商業秘密嘅理由。<br />\n<br />\n可口可樂嘅配方係商業秘密，可樂公司唔會公開。你飲可樂個罐知係糖，水，碳酸等一般成份。你攞罐可樂唔可以整返一罐同樣嘅飲品。Software同飲品唔同，如果open source，產品就係個配方，任何trade secret都唔會再係秘密。<br />\n<br />\n不過唔open source都唔一定可以保護trade secret，因為可以reverse engineering，但難度高好多。"},{"pid":"53b1376e11f62e753ffefd2f0c9af95bcdbbdaba","tid":299804,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T01:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>保護知識產權有唔同方法，可以用版權，專利話者用商業秘密（trade secret）。如果產品係open source，就唔可以用商業秘密嘅理由。<br />\n<br />\n可口可樂嘅配方係商業秘密，可樂公司唔會公開。你飲可樂個罐知係糖，水，碳酸等一般成份。你攞罐可樂唔可以整返一罐同樣嘅飲品。Software同飲品唔同，如果open source，產品就係個配方，任何trade secret都唔會再係秘密。<br />\n<br />\n不過唔open source都唔一定可以保護trade secret，因為可以reverse engineering，但難度高好多。</blockquote><br />\nsorry，回錯post。"},{"pid":"f4f25bc08060e762ae5c4d1fd51e95f70c0a0ef8","tid":299804,"uid":80035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca5db67a4d34156a33e55a689f25197411152f6","tid":299804,"uid":80035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:54:31.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打順便講下行業趨勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22278a9ac0dfc80f4b9ef520ee481d12